name: Jessy: Ascending Star FUTANARI EDITION [XXX Complete Miningame]
name_original: Jessy: Ascending Star FUTANARI EDITION [XXX Complete Miningame]
description:
In this game you impersonate Jessy, a young girl looking for luck who works as a bartender. Jessy's dream has always been to end her economic problems. A routine life that will change one evening when you meet a mysterious person entering the bar where you work. What will a good girl be willing to do for money?

What's different in the Futanari Edition?
The main character is actually a Futanari!
